    <h3>Translation notes</h3>
    <p>The harmonic series diverges slowly: 10,000 terms only reaches about 9.8. Our numerical partial sums illustrate convergence speed but cannot prove convergence or divergence. The comparison test is a proof technique, not a computation.</p>

